## Full Pipeline

1. Read `{{INSTRUCTION_FILE}}`, `README.md`, `design/current-system-design.md`, and `design/core-skills-spec.md`.
2. Treat `skill-pack.json`, `SKILL.md.tmpl`, the root skill directories, and `prompt-templates/` as the source of truth for agent-facing assets.
3. If the request concerns unconfigured ongoing tracking, route through `topic-curation` before digest or deep-analysis behavior.
4. For ongoing tracking requests, distinguish them from one-off research, handle recurring automation or scheduling before any digest output, and ask whether the user wants a test run instead of running one automatically.
5. When skill or prompt behavior changes, regenerate the installable skill pack with `python -m skrya_orchestrator.main build-skill-pack --root . --host all`.
6. Update tests and docs together with the behavior change.
7. Before finishing, run the full unittest suite and report the verification result.

